@aishaazmi Hi there, 
We’re sorry to hear that your luggage wasn't duly delivered. Please send us your reference number via PM, so we can take a closer look. Thank you for your patience and understanding.
Best regards, Shawn

@mirasc79 Hello Miras, 
I'm sorry to hear you haven't received a response yet. Please send us the reference number of your claim via DM (XXXX-OS-XXXXX) and we'll have a closer look.
Best regards, Gayle

@brem_erez Hello Erez,
thanks for reaching out. Have you been in contact with our Feedback Management? If yes, then please continue corresponding with them as we, the Social Media Team do not handle claims. 
Best regards, Gayle

@miss_rosiiie Hello there Miss Rosie,
you can add the baggage on our webpage or at the airport.
Best regards, Alessandra

@tuxford_jacob Dear Jacob,
I'm sorry that you are already waiting for so long. Please send me your file reference number XXXX-OS-XXXXXX so we can have a closer look at your complaint. 
Kind regards, Alessandra

@rossenbe1 Hello Marion, 
I'm sorry to hear you haven't received a response yet. Please send us the reference number (XXXX-OS-XXXXX) of your claim via DM and we'll check if your request has been forwarded to the respective department. 
Best regards, Gayle

@sekerova Hello Zuzana,
Thank you for your patience till now. We'll forward your reference number to our respective department with a note of urgency. Please be aware that even prioritized cases will need some time.
Kind regards, Alessandra

@Tacticalan Hi Alan, I apologize for the inconvenience you had to experience during your journey. 
To bring your inquiry to notice I kindly ask you to fill out our online form on https://t.co/vmBr0ynoFt. 
Best regards, Denis

@rsamii Hello Roxanna, 
